summary: LOST, 2018 (final page) start from the beginning   Thank you for reading, everyone !! This was just a little project but I want...
caption:
LOST, 2018 (final page)

start from the beginning  

Thank you for reading, everyone !! This was just a little project but I want to keep creating comics in the future. I’ve wanted to make them since I was younger, but I guess now I feel I have enough experience or skill to do it, and I want to share it with you guys since I’ve just been showing my illustrations up until now!

(*´ｪ｀*)

Feel free to follow me on my other social media to get more frequent updates, check out my online store, or read the whole comic from the start!
